IMPATIENCE

38
00:02:18,097 --> 00:02:20,224
<i>N... He's similar...</i>

39
00:02:20,892 --> 00:02:23,019
<i>This feeling. . .is like L...</i>

40
00:02:23,436 --> 00:02:25,355
<i>I said we will
no longer rely on L...</i>

41
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:30,526
<i>That means,
my orders to the CIA and FBI</i>

42
00:02:30,610 --> 00:02:32,654
<i>will be given priority over L's.</i>

43
00:02:33,446 --> 00:02:36,574
<i>However, the murder of
the Director of the NPA</i>

44
00:02:36,658 --> 00:02:38,326
<i>is an unforgivable crime...</i>

45
00:02:38,785 --> 00:02:40,662
I think there is a possibility

46
00:02:40,745 --> 00:02:44,290
