to the arrest of Kira...

47
00:02:44,457 --> 00:02:46,668
So I will lend you my full support.

48
00:02:47,335 --> 00:02:50,380
<i>"Lead to the arrest of Kira?"
Who does he think he is?</i>

49
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:51,714
<i>This confidence...</i>

50
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,800
<i>What's wrong, L?</i>

51
00:02:54,092 --> 00:02:55,218
N-Nothing.

52
00:02:55,927 --> 00:02:58,137
Actually, after the director
was murdered...

53
00:02:58,304 --> 00:03:00,390
Deputy Director Yagami's daughter
was kidnapped by someone...

54
00:03:00,556 --> 00:03:02,934
